{"tid":1736884,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"喺生死關頭嘅時候你會諗起邊個？","createTime":"2019-11-18T21:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T08:53:32.000Z","uid":276622,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f15e100130035a5771f468a249ed496302da0f","tid":1736884,"uid":276622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T21:47:54.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢仆街爭啲畀狗咬，嗰陣係到諗 我唔想死住<br />\n事後諗起當初中四鍾意嘅女仔，好後悔中六嗰陣冇去表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然而家有時都會諗返起佢，但係無謂再去打搞到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪人都會係最後關頭先會諗返起自己嘅遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">每次見到有手足比狗咬，都好自責自己係咪做到未夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a5fc1862d29c70ec0aec8bc70e63b8a14fa6fd8c","tid":1736884,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:52:13.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n因為我根本唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea98f5e006ff3cc7c82c91d7201234c768fa7da4","tid":1736884,"uid":79273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:55:32.000Z","msg":"逃跑既時候一路諗住ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993cb66cb77796e90b8b8dfaa9756304e3b4bbf0","tid":1736884,"uid":14305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:56:36.000Z","msg":"比狗咬過一次 <br />\n個腦空白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f597e83703667bf3322fdf560f833e3f05b20a","tid":1736884,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:53:27.000Z","msg":"諗起分咗手個幾星期既佢"},{"pid":"a4550320b9e4112a66c3e004add161ee0026fccb","tid":1736884,"uid":157913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T00:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14df28fcb3